MeeMee Car Seat Cum Carry Cot (Light Blue) Price: Rs.4795

Using car seats when travelling with small children in cars and other similar vehicles is always safer than holding them in ones arms. The Mee Mee Car Seat cum Carry Cot has been designed to provide the best possible protection to your child with utmost comfort. This Car Seat from Mee Mee is suitable for children from birth. Your infant will be protected from any kind of impact from the side by the deep and softly padded side wings that act as side impact protector.\xa0The performance chest pads will serve as extra protection to your infant's body. This has a three-point harness that will keep your tiny tot safely buckled in her seat. The harness retainers on this Mee Mee Car Seat will enable you to seat your darling and lift her up from the seat easily.

An interesting feature of this Car Seat from Mee Mee is that it can be converted to a baby rocker when needed. You can carry this Car Seat using the carry handle that can be easily adjusted. To protect your little angel from sunlight there is a canopy and a head support pillow to give adequate support to her delicate neck. This Mee Mee Baby Car Seat cum Carry Cot sports a light weight of 2500 g.

Key Features

  • Detachable Weaning Tray

The Mee Mee Baby Pram is a comprehensive travel system that comes with a range of features to give your baby the best possible comfort. This baby buggy can be used for children between the ages of 0 and 36 months. The maximum weight that the Mee Mee Pram can support is 15 kg. The seat on the Mee Mee Pram is integrated with a multi-position reclining feature that optimizes your baby’s comfort. A mosquito net that is attached to this baby carrier’s seat helps in covering your infant. Your little angel will be safe in the Mee Mee Pram with its five-point harness.

Weighing just up to 3 kg and with dimensions 550 x 1200 x 990 mm this ultra-light Mee Mee Pram can be folded compactly and stored. Your tiny tot will have a jerk-free journey in this Pram as the lockable front wheels have suspension in them. The ergonomic reversible foam handles let you face your baby while steering the pram. The weaning tray is detachable and the large shopping basket in the Mee Mee Pram lets you store your baby’s accessories effortlessly and within your arm’s reach.

MeeMee Baby Carrier (Blue) Price: Rs.995

Key Features

  • Safe

Baby carriers help you in carrying your bundle of joy along with you but without tiring your arms. These baby carriers will help in taking off the weight from your arms and give you freedom to move about more freely. The Mee Mee Baby Carrier that conforms to high safety standards is suitable for children from the age of three months. The detachable head support on the Mee Mee Baby Carrier helps in providing that extra support needed to keep your darling’s delicate neck upright.

This easy fitting Baby Carrier from Mee Mee has spacious leg and arm holes that allow your infant to effortlessly accommodate her tiny limbs in the Mee Mee Carrier. The cozy cushioned inner seat of the Mee Mee Carrier makes sure that your little darling get the best possible comfort while travelling. With the adjustable padded shoulder straps you will not feel the burden of the baby’s weight weighing down on your shoulders. You can choose to seat your baby in two varying positions and also face the child inwards or outwards depending on your preference. The machine washable breathable fabric of the Mee Mee Baby Carrier allows proper ventilation for the toddler seated in it.
